1
00:00:06,836 --> 00:00:11,273
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

2
00:00:11,340 --> 00:00:14,867
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

3
00:00:14,944 --> 00:00:18,380
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

4
00:00:18,447 --> 00:00:22,042
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way</i>

5
00:00:22,118 --> 00:00:25,383
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

6
00:00:25,454 --> 00:00:27,388
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>

7
00:00:29,192 --> 00:00:32,127
<i>Down a difficult road</i>
<i>filled with endless struggles</i>

8
00:00:32,195 --> 00:00:35,995
<i>Where do you think you are going</i>
<i>following someone else's map?</i>

9
00:00:36,399 --> 00:00:43,237
<i>An insightful crow comes along</i>
<i>to tear up the map</i>

10
00:00:43,472 --> 00:00:50,537
<i>Now open your eyes and</i>
<i>take a look at the truth (Yeah!)</i>

11
00:00:50,846 --> 00:00:56,978
<i>There's nothing to lose,</i>
<i>so let's GO!!!</i>

12
00:00:57,119 --> 00:01:01,385
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

13
00:01:01,457 --> 00:01:05,052
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

14
00:01:05,127 --> 00:01:08,460
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

15
00:01:08,531 --> 00:01:12,160
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh!</i>
<i>Just go my way</i>

16
00:01:12,235 --> 00:01:15,830
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

17
00:01:15,905 --> 00:01:19,397
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best!</i>

18
00:01:19,475 --> 00:01:23,070
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

19
00:01:23,145 --> 00:01:27,241
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!</i>

20
00:01:33,266 --> 00:01:36,201
<i>Unforgivable! A Total Lack of Respect!</i>

21
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:57,686
W-What the heck is going on here?

22
00:01:58,858 --> 00:01:59,688
Hmm...

23
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:01,090
Help me!

24
00:02:02,528 --> 00:02:04,758
Excuse me there, Mister!
Wait just a moment!

25
00:02:05,598 --> 00:02:06,963
What in the world is happening?

26
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:09,031
You should run away too!

27
00:02:09,202 --> 00:02:10,794
There's a monster up there!

28
00:02:11,771 --> 00:02:12,863
A monster...?

29
00:02:13,239 --> 00:02:15,969
What could it be?
This monster thing?!

30
00:02:16,409 --> 00:02:20,846
It's a g-gigantic snake!
It destroyed the castle in a flash!

31
00:02:23,916 --> 00:02:25,747
How big of a snake?!

32
00:02:25,818 --> 00:02:28,514
Me too, at my village before...

33
00:02:28,621 --> 00:02:31,112
I was attacked by a huge snake!

34
00:02:31,190 --> 00:02:32,487
We must hurry, Naruto!

35
00:02:33,659 --> 00:02:37,493
That snake is probably the same one
that you saw before.

36
00:02:49,542 --> 00:02:51,339
Destroy the Leaf Village...?!

37
00:03:03,356 --> 00:03:04,482
And your answer is?

38
00:03:18,304 --> 00:03:19,464
Lady Tsunade!

39
00:03:20,573 --> 00:03:23,474
No! You must not believe
in their sweet talk...

40
00:03:24,177 --> 00:03:28,341
Your brother and my uncle
wouldn't want any of that!

41
00:03:29,015 --> 00:03:30,448
Their wishes...

42
00:03:30,983 --> 00:03:33,781
Moreover, Tsunade, your wishes...

43
00:03:33,853 --> 00:03:36,321
And dreams...
Did you forget them?!

44
00:03:41,127 --> 00:03:42,924
I know it!

45
00:03:43,696 --> 00:03:46,426
Even if you are like this now,
you still...

46
00:03:49,268 --> 00:03:51,532
Open your eyes! Wake up, please!

47
00:03:51,604 --> 00:03:52,866
Shut up, Shizune!

48
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:14,048
You don't have to answer right now.

49
00:04:15,428 --> 00:04:17,623
However, I want it in a week.

50
00:04:18,664 --> 00:04:22,225
Also, two human sacrifices are needed
for this Forbidden Jutsu,

51
00:04:23,002 --> 00:04:25,698
so do what you need to do
to prepare them.

52
00:04:28,174 --> 00:04:32,076
Lady Tsunade, let's kill them right here!
It's our chance!

53
00:04:32,211 --> 00:04:35,203
With you and me, now we can...!

54
00:04:41,787 --> 00:04:42,811
<i>Lady Tsunade...</i>

55
00:05:20,293 --> 00:05:23,126
Sure, I am weak now.

56
00:05:23,462 --> 00:05:24,360
However...

57
00:05:27,333 --> 00:05:30,700
I also know Tsunade's weakness.

58
00:05:32,138 --> 00:05:36,097
<i>That's right, he is one of the Sannin</i>
<i>like Tsunade.</i>

59
00:05:37,210 --> 00:05:38,074
<i>So he knows that...</i>

60
00:05:41,214 --> 00:05:43,910
I see it's not cured yet...

61
00:05:45,751 --> 00:05:47,878
your fear of blood.

62
00:05:50,289 --> 00:05:51,779
<i>Hemophobia...?</i>

63
00:05:55,928 --> 00:05:58,590
Shall we get going, Kabuto?

64
00:06:00,666 --> 00:06:05,763
Tsunade... I'll be expecting
a favorable answer from you.

65
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:33,364
Looks like we were a little too late...

66
00:06:36,002 --> 00:06:37,333
Is this that snake's doing, too?!

67
00:06:37,637 --> 00:06:39,229
- Let's go, Naruto!
- Huh?

68
00:06:39,305 --> 00:06:41,000
Tsunade isn't here any more.

69
00:06:41,741 --> 00:06:44,539
Geez, you keep telling me that...!

70
00:06:54,287 --> 00:06:55,254
Welcome!

71
00:06:55,321 --> 00:06:57,812
Hey, you ol' man, give me another shot!

72
00:06:58,057 --> 00:07:00,218
Lady Tsunade, you're drinking too much!

73
00:07:07,533 --> 00:07:08,465
Lady Tsunade...

74
00:07:10,970 --> 00:07:13,666
Heck, she's nowhere to be found!

75
00:07:14,340 --> 00:07:16,934
Dragging me around here and there,

76
00:07:17,243 --> 00:07:19,803
but after all,
we haven't found a single trace!

77
00:07:20,413 --> 00:07:21,209
Hmm?

78
00:07:23,215 --> 00:07:25,706
Well, let's dine here for now.

79
00:07:25,851 --> 00:07:26,510
Huh?

80
00:07:26,786 --> 00:07:29,755
Isn't this a pub?

81
00:07:30,356 --> 00:07:32,085
So what?

82
00:07:32,458 --> 00:07:36,485
I've told you so many times!
I'm still underage!

83
00:07:36,662 --> 00:07:42,692
You fool. Nobody is asking you to drink.
Kids should only be eating snacks.

84
00:07:43,669 --> 00:07:44,601
- Well then...
- Welcome!

85
00:07:44,670 --> 00:07:46,865
There's no need to dine here!

86
00:07:47,173 --> 00:07:48,663
We can go to a ramen noodle shop
or something!

87
00:07:48,741 --> 00:07:53,178
How stupid! You can gather information
in this type of place...

88
00:08:00,252 --> 00:08:00,911
Huh?

89
00:08:01,687 --> 00:08:02,483
Huh?!

90
00:08:04,056 --> 00:08:05,421
Tsunade!

91
00:08:06,225 --> 00:08:07,249
Jiraiya?!

92
00:08:07,927 --> 00:08:10,054
Why... are you here?

93
00:08:10,396 --> 00:08:14,196
I've finally found you!
I'm exhausted...

94
00:08:15,434 --> 00:08:17,425
<i>That gal is Tsunade?!</i>

95
00:08:23,109 --> 00:08:25,009
<i>She's 50 years old for real?</i>

96
00:08:26,412 --> 00:08:27,401
<i>Now, that's a swindle.</i>

97
00:08:33,052 --> 00:08:36,579
<i>I can't believe...</i>
<i>I met two of the Sannin in one day.</i>

98
00:08:40,493 --> 00:08:41,858
Here you are!

99
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:59,739
In any case...
Today is a day I see many old friends.

100
00:09:09,955 --> 00:09:11,445
You mean Orochimaru...

101
00:09:13,893 --> 00:09:15,087
What happened?

102
00:09:18,564 --> 00:09:22,557
Nothing, really.
We exchanged a greeting.

103
00:09:39,385 --> 00:09:42,218
<i>Is it really true that this gal</i>
<i>is the Kunoichi</i>

104
00:09:42,288 --> 00:09:45,189
<i>who can heal any kind of wound?</i>

105
00:09:46,892 --> 00:09:47,916
What about you?

106
00:09:48,527 --> 00:09:50,256
What do you want from me?

107
00:09:54,333 --> 00:09:55,698
I'll be straight with you.

108
00:10:01,841 --> 00:10:07,438
Tsunade, the village has demanded
that you become the Fifth Hokage.

109
00:10:17,723 --> 00:10:21,181
Hey, ol' man,
gimme the simmered meat with potatoes!

110
00:10:21,260 --> 00:10:22,488
All right, in a moment.

111
00:10:32,738 --> 00:10:35,832
<i>The Fifth Hokage?!</i>
<i>What's this out of the blue?!</i>

112
00:10:35,908 --> 00:10:37,899
<i>What the heck is going on?!</i>

113
00:10:42,281 --> 00:10:44,181
Do you know about the Third Hokage!?

114
00:10:46,185 --> 00:10:49,882
<i>The Third Hokage?</i>
<i>So, he really was...</i>

115
00:10:56,328 --> 00:10:58,296
Orochimaru did it, right?

116
00:10:59,331 --> 00:11:02,391
I heard about it.
Directly from him.

117
00:11:03,469 --> 00:11:05,164
<i>Orochimaru did it...?</i>

118
00:11:06,472 --> 00:11:07,461
Orochimaru?!

119
00:11:07,573 --> 00:11:09,803
Did he really killed the old man,
the Third Hokage?!

120
00:11:09,975 --> 00:11:11,840
Who is this Orochimaru?!

121
00:11:13,012 --> 00:11:16,675
Just like us, he's one of the Sannin.

122
00:11:17,249 --> 00:11:20,776
Why?! The Sannin are all
from Leaf Village, right?

123
00:11:20,853 --> 00:11:22,013
Then why?!

124
00:11:22,555 --> 00:11:24,045
Who's this brat?

125
00:11:28,561 --> 00:11:30,620
He's Naruto Uzumaki.

126
00:11:33,465 --> 00:11:36,298
<i>This brat is...</i>
<i>that Nine Tailed Fox...?</i>

127
00:11:36,769 --> 00:11:38,293
Hey, you just hold it there!

128
00:11:39,305 --> 00:11:42,069
I am not done talking yet!

129
00:11:43,008 --> 00:11:46,637
This Orochimaru?!
This bastard that killed Old Man Hokage.

130
00:11:46,845 --> 00:11:48,676
Who the heck is he?!

131
00:11:48,948 --> 00:11:51,712
He's a legendary Sannin, right?!

132
00:11:52,084 --> 00:11:53,813
Then knowing that...

133
00:11:53,886 --> 00:11:55,979
why would you, Pervy Sage,
leave such a guy alone?!

134
00:11:56,522 --> 00:11:57,546
Besides...

135
00:11:57,623 --> 00:12:00,114
What do you mean this person
is the Fifth Hokage?!

136
00:12:00,192 --> 00:12:02,490
Naruto, be quiet for a moment.

137
00:12:02,561 --> 00:12:03,755
But...!

138
00:12:04,463 --> 00:12:06,090
Just shut up!

139
00:12:30,489 --> 00:12:32,013
I'll say this again.

140
00:12:33,559 --> 00:12:39,395
They are demanding that
you become the Fifth Hokage, Tsunade.

141
00:12:45,571 --> 00:12:47,664
So what's your answer?

142
00:12:57,249 --> 00:12:59,217
Will you accept it?

143
00:13:04,857 --> 00:13:09,920
<i>I'll resurrect the little brother</i>
<i>and man, both of whom you loved...</i>

144
00:13:12,531 --> 00:13:17,025
<i>This time, I will completely destroy Leaf!</i>

145
00:13:30,516 --> 00:13:33,713
What do you say... Tsunade?

146
00:13:38,223 --> 00:13:39,281
<i>Lady Tsunade...</i>

147
00:13:42,761 --> 00:13:44,490
<i>I really don't get it!</i>

148
00:13:54,907 --> 00:13:56,169
Impossible...

149
00:13:58,410 --> 00:13:59,274
I refuse!

150
00:14:07,319 --> 00:14:10,117
I remember... those words.

151
00:14:11,023 --> 00:14:15,790
You said those same words
when I asked you to go out with me.

152
00:14:17,362 --> 00:14:21,924
What the heck are you talking about?!
You said it yourself!

153
00:14:22,167 --> 00:14:23,930
Didn't you say that
you will bring her back to the village

154
00:14:24,002 --> 00:14:26,527
and have her treat Sasuke
and Kakashi Sensei?!

155
00:14:26,605 --> 00:14:29,096
But what's this demand
for her to be the Hokage?!

156
00:14:29,174 --> 00:14:30,971
And, on top of that, she refuses!

157
00:14:33,479 --> 00:14:34,411
<i>Lady Tsunade...</i>

158
00:14:34,713 --> 00:14:37,307
<i>Could she be thinking of making</i>
<i>a deal with Orochimaru?</i>

159
00:14:42,421 --> 00:14:43,979
Calm down.

160
00:14:44,056 --> 00:14:46,718
There can't be no other Fifth Hokage,
but this Tsunade.

161
00:14:49,094 --> 00:14:51,085
During the dreadful Great War Era,

162
00:14:51,163 --> 00:14:53,597
she contributed tremendously
to the Leaf's victory.

163
00:14:57,102 --> 00:14:58,296
To this date,

164
00:14:58,370 --> 00:15:02,170
there's no one who can rival
her combat and medical skills.

165
00:15:03,909 --> 00:15:07,242
Still more, this Tsunade is
the granddaughter of the First Hokage

166
00:15:07,713 --> 00:15:09,112
So together with her talents,

167
00:15:09,181 --> 00:15:13,208
there's no one else more suited
to becoming the Fifth Hokage

168
00:15:14,787 --> 00:15:16,152
If she becomes Hokage,

169
00:15:16,221 --> 00:15:18,018
that means that
she'll come back to the village

170
00:15:19,424 --> 00:15:23,690
And then, as I'd told you,
she can treat the two.

171
00:15:24,429 --> 00:15:29,366
Besides, this is what the Leaf's
top decision-making advisors settled upon.

172
00:15:30,269 --> 00:15:35,002
Genin like you have no say
on this matter.

173
00:15:37,543 --> 00:15:38,510
Jiraiya...

174
00:15:39,645 --> 00:15:42,011
Unlike your previous apprentice,

175
00:15:42,080 --> 00:15:45,345
this kid not only has a bad mouth and wit,
he's ugly to match.

176
00:15:45,617 --> 00:15:46,515
What?!

177
00:15:46,885 --> 00:15:50,719
It's tough on anyone to be
compared to the Fourth Hokage.

178
00:15:51,423 --> 00:15:55,621
He had all the qualities to be
the greatest Ninja in all history.

179
00:15:56,094 --> 00:15:58,927
Brimming with talent in Jutsu,
and he had a brilliant mind!

180
00:15:59,131 --> 00:16:04,000
Popular with people and well...
he was as handsome as me.

181
00:16:04,469 --> 00:16:07,632
But even that Fourth Hokage died quickly.

182
00:16:09,007 --> 00:16:12,443
Risking his own life for the village...

183
00:16:17,349 --> 00:16:18,873
Life is different from money...

184
00:16:22,921 --> 00:16:26,516
To easily risk it and lose it,
is a fool's doing!

185
00:16:32,231 --> 00:16:33,289
<i>Did she say "fool"?!</i>

186
00:16:34,800 --> 00:16:37,030
Both my grandfather and the Second Hokage

187
00:16:37,102 --> 00:16:40,367
seemed to want to subdue
the disturbances of war above all else.

188
00:16:41,306 --> 00:16:43,206
But after all, they died in vain,

189
00:16:43,275 --> 00:16:45,971
in the midst of their dreams
for the village.

190
00:16:50,349 --> 00:16:51,577
You have changed, Tsunade...

191
00:16:51,650 --> 00:16:55,142
I don't know what
you thought in your heart before,

192
00:16:55,520 --> 00:16:56,953
but to say such thing out loud...

193
00:17:00,092 --> 00:17:02,526
Although I look young,
I'm already in my 50s...

194
00:17:03,128 --> 00:17:04,993
Years change people.

195
00:17:12,571 --> 00:17:14,334
Same goes for Sarutobi Sensei...

196
00:17:15,407 --> 00:17:19,275
No wonder he died showing off
at that old age!

197
00:17:41,633 --> 00:17:43,123
Hokage is a bother.

198
00:17:43,201 --> 00:17:45,226
No one but a fool would take it on.

199
00:17:49,207 --> 00:17:50,174
Why you?!

200
00:17:50,242 --> 00:17:52,608
- Let go of me!
- Don't! We're in a pub.

201
00:17:53,011 --> 00:17:54,706
I said, let go of me!

202
00:17:55,514 --> 00:17:56,310
Lady Tsunade!

203
00:17:58,650 --> 00:18:02,450
Anyone who makes fun of the old man
and the Fourth Hokage...

204
00:18:02,521 --> 00:18:04,216
It doesn't matter if
you are a woman!

205
00:18:05,023 --> 00:18:07,890
I'll clobber you with all my might!

206
00:18:16,635 --> 00:18:20,196
You're pretty gutsy...
confronting me like this.

207
00:18:22,007 --> 00:18:23,804
Let's take this outside, brat!

208
00:18:24,109 --> 00:18:25,007
Lady Tsunade!

209
00:18:38,357 --> 00:18:41,520
Though I may not look it,
I am one of the Sannin.

210
00:18:43,996 --> 00:18:45,987
Why should I even take a Genin seriously.

211
00:18:46,598 --> 00:18:47,860
What did you say?!

212
00:18:53,505 --> 00:18:54,995
An advance notice for a KO?

213
00:18:55,273 --> 00:18:56,467
I don't mean one minute...

214
00:18:57,075 --> 00:19:01,842
With one finger.
This is enough to take you down.

215
00:19:02,147 --> 00:19:03,205
Lady Tsunade!

216
00:19:03,715 --> 00:19:04,739
Well...

217
00:19:05,450 --> 00:19:07,111
Come on, kiddo.

218
00:19:08,720 --> 00:19:10,745
D-Don't make fun of me!

219
00:19:20,866 --> 00:19:22,094
<i>Darn it!</i>

220
00:19:29,541 --> 00:19:30,473
Lady Tsunade!

221
00:19:36,114 --> 00:19:37,206
<i>Forehead poking?!</i>

222
00:19:37,983 --> 00:19:39,041
<i>Why that no good!</i>

223
00:19:45,590 --> 00:19:46,579
<i>She's strong...</i>

224
00:19:48,460 --> 00:19:49,484
Hey, brat!

225
00:19:50,996 --> 00:19:53,464
I'll ask you one thing before you faint.

226
00:19:56,034 --> 00:20:00,198
Why... get so passionate at
the mention of Hokage's name?

227
00:20:05,944 --> 00:20:08,378
Unlike you...

228
00:20:09,147 --> 00:20:11,911
I will be the heir to the Hokage name,
no matter what!

229
00:20:14,252 --> 00:20:15,583
Because Hokage is...

230
00:20:17,622 --> 00:20:20,386
Because Hokage is my dream!

231
00:20:24,696 --> 00:20:25,594
That kid...

232
00:20:33,371 --> 00:20:35,498
<i>What? She's a bit off her guard...</i>

233
00:20:36,074 --> 00:20:37,871
<i>I can't tackle her head on.</i>

234
00:20:38,343 --> 00:20:39,901
<i>Then, I should use that Jutsu now...</i>

235
00:20:40,479 --> 00:20:41,639
<i>Concentrate!</i>

236
00:20:53,758 --> 00:20:54,656
<i>Oh, no!</i>

237
00:20:55,994 --> 00:20:58,121
<i>Wha?! This Jutsu is...!</i>

238
00:20:58,697 --> 00:21:01,222
Take this!

239
00:21:06,705 --> 00:21:11,404
<i>I believe your promise,</i>
<i>its a true heart give me courage</i>

240
00:21:11,476 --> 00:21:15,810
<i>Always I feel it</i>
<i>the precious time with you</i>

241
00:21:16,415 --> 00:21:19,942
<i>On your still shoulder</i>

242
00:21:21,186 --> 00:21:25,646
<i>I feel the wind that blows</i>
<i>towards tomorrow</i>

243
00:21:25,824 --> 00:21:31,262
<i>The city lights are like pieces of stars</i>

244
00:21:31,763 --> 00:21:36,063
<i>That hold us together</i>

245
00:21:36,535 --> 00:21:45,773
<i>"Each one of us glows differently,"</i>

246
00:21:45,844 --> 00:21:48,438
<i>you say laughingly</i>

247
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:54,346
<i>but you look most dazzling</i>

248
00:21:54,920 --> 00:21:59,289
<i>Like a comet,</i>

249
00:21:59,358 --> 00:22:05,456
<i>like the rainbow after the storm</i>

250
00:22:05,530 --> 00:22:12,629
<i>You bring light into my heart</i>

251
00:22:13,638 --> 00:22:23,013
<i>Being lost can be the answer</i>

252
00:22:24,349 --> 00:22:31,881
<i>Let's promise we won't cheat</i>

253
00:22:31,957 --> 00:22:35,950
<i>Uh...like a shooting star,</i>
<i>we do go ahead.</i>

254
00:22:38,463 --> 00:22:41,796
It's been a long time since we drank
alone like this, isn't it, Tsunade?

255
00:22:41,867 --> 00:22:43,960
I didn't necessarily want to see you.

256
00:22:44,036 --> 00:22:45,128
Don't say that.

257
00:22:45,270 --> 00:22:47,568
By the way,
you're prettier than before.

258
00:22:47,639 --> 00:22:48,936
You haven't changed a bit.

259
00:22:49,241 --> 00:22:52,108
Understand this.
I'm not interested in you.

260
00:22:52,177 --> 00:22:55,874
Neither am I.
After all, you're actually 50 years old

261
00:22:55,947 --> 00:22:57,278
- Did you say something
- No, nothing

262
00:22:57,349 --> 00:22:59,909
I was just remembering
the old days.

263
00:23:00,385 --> 00:23:04,287
Next time: "Inheritance!
"The Necklace of Death!"
